{\n  "title": "Fix: resilient login/signup without Firebase",\n  "body": "This PR fixes the login system by adding in-memory fallbacks when Firebase is unavailable, and makes Elara/Vero Firestore-optional.\n\nChanges:\n- Auth: safe in-memory user store and metrics fallback\n- Elara: guard Firestore access with availability checks\n- Vero: guard Firestore access and context retrieval\n- Tests: backend/test.py validates signup+login flow\n\nManual test results:\n- Signup: 201 Created\n- Login: 200 OK, returns user + metrics\n- Greeting + Resource endpoints: 200 OK\n",\n  "head": "fix/auth-fallbacks",\n  "base": "main"\n}\n